"§ 90-210.28B. Penalties.
(a) In any case in which Authorization. – If the Board is entitled to suspend, revoke
revoke, or refuse to renew a license, license or permit, the Board may accept from the licensee
or permit holder an offer to pay a civil penalty of not more than five thousand dollars ($5,000).
